    "Name": "Rifleman IIC",
    "Details": "This Mech, apparently Won Through a Batchall against Clanners, was Mildly Upgraded with Inner Sphere Tech. Each Arm has a Clan RAC5 and a Small Xpulse Laser, the Torso has a MRM10 each. With enough Ammo to Last Two Battles, this Rifleman still serves its Original Purpose. It's fast and Armoured too, with a Serious Ewar Package. Dont think this Clan mech is as Feeble as its Predecessors.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Integrated Searchlight</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.21</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
